:::


We display the most expensive items in Animal Crossing below: 


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
items %>% 
  top_n(10, buy_value) %>%
  arrange(desc(buy_value)) %>%
  select(name, sell_value, buy_value, category, image=image_url) %>%
  gt() %>%
   text_transform(
     #tell gt that the image column 
    locations = cells_body(vars(image)),
    fn = function(x) {
      web_image(
        url = x,
        height = 50
      )
    }
  )
```

